  "title": "Retail Customer Service (Japanese-speaking)【Up to $4,000】",
  "description": "<p>【Job ID: 1110079】</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Respond to customer enquiries via WhatsApp</li><li>Explain purchasing processes clearly and professionally</li><li>Prepare quotations, invoices, and related documentation</li><li>Verify the authenticity of incoming luxury items and jewellery</li><li>Provide simple translation support as needed</li><li>Perform other assigned duties</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>No prior experience required; training will be provided</li><li>Proficiency in Japanese (JLPT N4 or above) for liaising with Japanese-speaking clients and stakeholders</li><li>Strong work ethic and punctuality</li><li>Willingness to work on weekends</li><li>Positive attitude and ability to work in a fast-paced environment</li></ul><p>——————————-</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. However, rest assured that all applications will be updated to our resume bank for future opportunities.</p><p>Please kindly refer to the Privacy Policy of Good Job Creations for your reference: https://goodjobcreations.com.sg/en/privacy-policy/</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Ito (Sherpa) Yurika</p><p>EA Personnel Registration Number: R25159178</p><p>EA License No.: 07C5771</p>",
